Ukrainian Mine Explosion Kills 16, Injures 2, Ministry Says

-- B y   H e n r y   M e y e r
-- 
2011-07-29T04:34:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-29/ukrainian-mine-explosion-kills-16-injures-2-ministry-says-1-.html
An explosion at a Ukrainian coal
mine in the Lugansk region killed 16 and left 2 workers
hospitalized, the Emergency Ministry said.  Ten miners are missing after a blast at 1:57 a.m. local
time, the ministry said in a statement on its website today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Henry Meyer in Moscow at 
